  <summary date="2022-02-01T19:36:36Z" status="Introduced in Senate">Prohibiting IRS Financial Surveillance Act 

This bill prohibits the Department of the Treasury from requiring a financial institution to report the balances, transactions, or the transfers into and out of a financial account. This prohibition does not apply to laws or regulations in effect on the date of enactment.</summary>
